272	## Step 8: Mobile Accessibility
273	
274	| Requirement | Implementation |
275	|---|---|
276	| Touch targets | `min-height: 48px` on all tappable elements (Material 3 minimum) |
277	| Interactive elements labeled | `aria-label="Close"` on icon buttons → `Semantics()` in Flutter |
278	| Active tab indicated | `data-selected="true"` on active nav destination |
279	| Navigation landmarks | `<nav class="bottom-nav">` → `NavigationBar` |
280	| Decorative content hidden | `aria-hidden="true"` on decorative icons → `excludeSemantics` |
281	| Reduced motion | `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)` → `MediaQuery.disableAnimations` |
282	| Heading hierarchy | Typography classes in logical order → `Semantics(header: true)` |
283	| Thumb reachability | Primary actions in bottom half of screen |
